<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Erfurt</head><p>Der Rat teilt wegen der Belastungen durch den Dekan und das Kapitel von St. Jakob in Bamberg mit, dass er zur Vermittlung bereit ist.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_436" id="217v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_436_r1l1">Erfürt </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_436_r1l2"><expan>Lieb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> frewnde / Als Jr vns <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> beſwe </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_436_r1l3">runge <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> / als <expan>etlıch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> den <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> geſchehe / als <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_436_r1l4"><expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan> Techant vnd Capıtel cʒü ſant Jacob cʒü <expan>Bamb<ex>er</ex>g</expan> etc </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_436_r1l5"><expan>Hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> brıefe wol <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nomen</expan> / . vnd <expan>laſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> ewr </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_436_r1l6">erſame <expan>frewntſch<ex>aft</ex></expan> <expan>wıſſe<ex>n</ex></expan> / daʒ ſie Jr <expan>botſch<ex>aft</ex></expan> bey vns </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_436_r1l7">gehabt vnd ſich vaſte <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>ewr<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> beklagt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_436_r1l8"><expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / . vnd vvir <expan>beſtellt<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / daʒ das den <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> geſagt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_436_r1l9">ward / daʒ ſie ſich darnach <expan>cʒerıcht<ex>e</ex>n</expan> weſten / vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_436_r1l10">wo das an vns köm künden wir dann ıht gütes <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_436_r1l11"><expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> dar cʒü gereden / <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> vvo wir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>erſamk<ex>eit</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_436_r1l12">lıeb dinſte vnd <expan>fruntſch<ex>aft</ex></expan> <expan>beweıſe<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>möht<ex>en</ex></expan> / Das <expan>tet<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_436_r1l13">wir <expan>allcʒ<ex>eit</ex></expan> mit wıllen <expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan> / <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ıj̃ . <expan>p<ex>oſt</ex></expan> Judıca </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_436" id="217v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Erfürt </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Lieb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> frewnde, als ir uns
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt
                                <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> beswerunge
                        <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>, als <expan>etlich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> den
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> geschehe als
                            <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan> techant und capitel czü sant Jacob czü
                                <expan>Bamb<ex>er</ex>g</expan> etc., <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
                        wir <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> briefe wol <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nomen</expan>
                        und <expan>lass<ex>en</ex></expan> ewr ersame
                            <expan>frewntsch<ex>aft</ex></expan>
<expan>wisse<ex>n</ex></expan>, daz sie ir <expan>botsch<ex>aft</ex></expan>
                        bey uns gehabt und sich vaste <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>ewr<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> beklagt <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>. Und wir
                                <expan>bestellt<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, daz das den
                            <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> gesagt ward, daz sie sich darnach
                            <expan>cze richt<ex>e</ex>n</expan> westen, und wo das an uns köm,
                        künden wir dann iht gütes <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> dar czü gereden <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan>
                        wo wir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>ersamk<ex>eit</ex></expan> lieb, dinste und
                                <expan>fruntsch<ex>aft</ex></expan>
<expan>beweise<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>möht<ex>en</ex></expan>, das <expan>tet<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir
                                <expan>allcz<ex>eit</ex></expan> mit willen
                            <expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan>. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ii
                                <expan>p<ex>ost</ex></expan> judica.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
